Get Ready for Agentforce
Learn how Agentforce fits your business goals, launch your first agent, and build a plan for AI success.

###About this Trail
Ready to bring the power of Agentforce into your business? This trail will walk you through understanding how AI and agents can transform your jobs, and how an Agentforce agent can increase productivity. Then, launch your very first agent! In order to set your team up for AI success, use the AI Strategy and Project Planning modules to identify top AI use cases at your company and get key stakeholders on board. Then, put together a plan to implement AI, bring in your data, and conduct a risk assessment.
